Description: Investigaciones Europeas de Dirección y Economía de la Empresa (European Research on Management and Business Economics) is a journal published every four months (January, May and September) by European Academy of Management and Business Economics (AEDEM) since 1995 (Spain). The aim of the Journal is to foster academic research and the spread of business knowledge by publishing original research works that deal with some specialities with relations in the fields of Economy and Business Management. The journal is indexed by SCOPUS, Thomson Reuters Emerging Sources Citation Index, EconLit, DOAJ, EBSCO Information Services, ULRICH'S Global Serials Directory, IBSS, ECONBIZ, ECONIS, ECONSTOR, Index Copernicus, REDALYC, e-Revistas, LATINDEX, DIALNET,ISOC-Economía, DICE, IN-RECS, RESH, MIAR, CARHUS, Academic Journals Database, CIRC, Cabell's Business Directories, Fuente Académica

